summary:
more thrones au! ft. pepper and rhodey, the dragon squad! and sam bucky nat, the cap squad! 

do not be fooled, the king may...
caption:
more thrones au! ft. pepper and rhodey, the dragon squad! and sam bucky nat, the cap squad!

do not be fooled, the king may rule the kingdom, but keep in mind, the dragon has three heads.

Pepper is the Hand of the King; Rhodey is the Lord Commander of the Kingsguard; Bucky and Nat are faceless men; Sam is a warg

more character backgrounds under the cut!

James Rhodes has known Tony Stark all his life, being highborn and close to the king and all. He was on his way of becoming a knight of the seven kingdoms when the king and queen died and the prince disappeared. Believing his best friend is not dead, Rhodey abandons his responsibilities to find him. 

And find him he did, with three growing dragons, and an ever growing army.

-

Virginia Potts was a merchant’s daughter who managed their small town in the outskirts of the free cities. Her life was turned upside down when the dothraki horde arrived, razed their town and took her as a slave. 

Anthony Stark then came and freed everyone, including her, but he only takes her in when she bravely criticized (insulted) his ruling style. Years later she is appointed Hand of the King.

-

The faceless men shall own no name, shall own no titles, shall own no face, but she likes it when he calls her Natalia, and he likes it when she calls him James.
